name: Gentle Courage
description: This large17 x 20 mm Pink Tourmaline is ehanced with a 6 mm Amethyst. It is set in Sterling Silver with Sterling stardust beads. It measures  2 1/4".

name: Karmic Evolution
description: This treasure is somewhat larger, measuring at a total of  4 inches. The top faceted stone is Neon Blue Apaptite, surrounded by pearls. The large crystal is a Phantom Quartz Crystal and is quite magnificent. It is sent in Argentium Sterling Silver.

name: Quiet Waters
description: This Sterling Silver pendant measures about 3" in total length. It features Larimar, London Blue Topaz and Pariaba Quartz. These three stones work well together giving an essence of peace and serenity.

name: Higher Purpose
description: This pendant feature a Blue Apatite and Orange Calcite center stone. This specimen was a new find for me during a recent gem show. It is enhanced with a London Blue Topaz 6 mm stone on the top and a Golden Sapphire briolette on the bottom. It is set in 14 k gold filled wire.

name: Golden Visionary
description: Wrapped in 14k Gold Filled wire, this creation has many unusual stones. The top stone is Golden Druzy Quartz, enhanced with Herkimer Diamond 6 mm faceted beads. The center stone is an Imperial Topaz and the bottom stone is Opal. From the top of the bail to the bottom of the pendant the measurement is 3 inches.

name: Joyful Balance
description: A Tiger Eye Buddha crowns Quartz Crystal beads and a Twin Quartz Crystal point. Said to energize, Tiger Eye is believed to provide strength through difficult times. It creates harmony between people with different view points. Quartz Crystal provides clarity and assists in healing, chakra opening, meditation  and spiritual enhancement and numerous other benefits. This pendant measures 3 1/4 inches and is designed with Argentium Sterling Silver.

name: Light Bridge
description: This necklace measures 22 inches and is adjustable. It features Aquamarine, Kyanite and Quartz Crystal. These stones aid in the activation of the throat chakra, facilitating communication. They promote telepathy between persons and transmit healing energy from one to the other making this a great piece for healers and lightworkers. The Quartz Crystals measure about 1 1/2" each.

name: Angel Within
description: This piece consists of a "Positive Quartz" cabachon stone measuring 3/4" by 1/2" enhanced with Herkimer Diamond faceted beads. Made entirely of Sterling Silver, it measures 20 inches long.

name: Hematite Drop Earrings
description: These earrings are about 2 1/2 inches long. They are sterling silver findings with a Hematite bead drop.

name: Aquamarine and Crystal Earrings
description: These earrings are almost 3 inches long in total length. They have Aquamarine and Quartz beads. The ear wire is sterling silver. Very light weight and easy to wear.

name: Copper Earrings
description: These earrings measure about 2 inches total. They have a sterling silver ear wire. The center stone is pure copper with copper beads on the top. The copper and green pearls are natural seed pearls with color enhancement.

name: Pearl Earrings
description: The total length of these earrings is about 2 inches. They have sterling silver ear wires and consist of a sterling hoop with freshwater pearls.

name: Pearl Drop Earrings
description: These earrings measure 2 inches total. They have sterling silver ear wires with a freshwater pearl.

name: Pretty in Pink
description: This necklace measures 18 inches with the pendant being 2 1/2 inches long. The necklace portion has Quartz Crystal beads and nuggets, Rose Quartz beads and pink and white pearls. The pendant consists of a Rainbow Moonstone carved face and a Rose Quartz cabachon. The wire used in this design is Argentium Sterling Silver. This piece truly has Luminescence.

name: Metallic Dream
description: This Copper and gemstone bracelet is 8 inches long. It has natural chunks of Pyrite and Copper. The beads are Pietersite, Carnelian and Jasper.

name: Over the Rainbow
description: The large stone at the bottom of this piece is Labradorite, enhanced with London Blue Topaz and Larimar. This is a larger piece, measuring 3 1/2 inches. Tap into your inner magical powers with this visionary stone.

name: Universal Healer
description: Moldavite is a treasured gem with mystic origins. Believed to be a tremendous healing stone it also connects  with your higher self and promotes psychic abilities. It's powerful attributes are too many to list. Quartz "Positive" stones are a crystal within a crystal. I believe that this as well as the faceted Andalusite and Labradorite beads complete this healing talisman.

name: Moon Maiden
description: A large  Rainbow Moostone is the focal point of this design. Blue Opal and a faceted Blue Apatite complete the pendant. Wrapped entirely in sterling silver, a special patterned wire encases the Moonstone and Opal. Rainbow Moonstone brings joy to one's energy field and helps deflect negativity. Blue Opal promotes a calm and centered mind while Blue Apatite has an uplifting energy.

name: Mind's Eye
description: Wrapped in round 14 k gold filled wire ( not gold plated) this Rutilated Quartz is enhanced with a Golden Tourmaline.The quartz is quite clear with beautiful golden rutile needles. Including the bail the total size is 2 inches. Rutilated quartz aids in receiving spiritual inspiration, activates the higher miind and helps to "lighten the load".  Golden Tourmaline promotes clear thinking and self worth.

name: Lucky Penny
description: This pendant was designed using 14 k gold filled wire. ( not gold plated) A golden pearl compliments a natural piece of copper. The length of the piece is 2 inches. Copper is believed to bring good luck to the wearer and can stimulate optimism.

name: Calypso Comet
description: This is a lariat style necklace. The clasp is in the front and consists of a silver piece latching into a natural geode slab. A handmade tassel of chains and glass beads, natural pearls, amethyst, aquamarine and hematite hangs from the bottom giving the piece movement. This is a 24 inch neckalce and the tassel is 4 inches.

name: The Atlantis
description: This necklace is 20 inches long, with sterling silver wire.  The shells are all natural as are the gemstones of chrysoprase, green quartz, aventurine, quartz crystal and pearls.

name: Crystal Blue Persuasion
description: Wrapped in 14 k gold filled wire ( not gold plated) this is a very unique piece. The large crystal stone is from Brazil. It is a crystal growing within a crystal.  Some believe that this stone will allow one to enable manifestation, goodness and light. This pendant is enhanced with a faceted Blue Topaz, the stone of inner guidance and truth.

name: Green Peace
description: This bracelet will fit a wrist size of 7 inches to 8 inches. It was made using 14 k gold fill wire ( not gold plated) and worked in a viking knit weave. Various hues of green glass beads are woven into the piece.

name: Glitter Diva
description: The piece was designed by channeling my " Inner Diva".  The wire used is Argentium Sterling silver. All of the stones are natural and include: Rainbow Moonstone, Sugelite, Amethyst, Silver Druzy Quartz,  Purple Druzy Quartz, Rose Quartz and Flourite. The neckalce is adjustable from 18 inches to 20 inches. This is a one of a kind piece and is entirely handcrafted.
